title: Vegas Baby
description: A Las Vegas doctor's controversial online contest sees anxious entrants vie for free in vitro fertilization, a procedure rarely covered by insurance.

title: Vikings Unearthed
description: Archaeologist Sarah Parcak follows clues to early Viking explorations and discusses just what these notoriously fierce warriors were really like.

title: Virgin School
description: Concerned that his virginity is a problem, a nervous 26-year-old enrolls in an intimacy program for sexually inexperienced men.

title: Virunga: Gorillas in Peril
description: The team behind the searing documentary reveals what inspired them to tell the story of Virunga and the lethal fight to save the gorillas' sanctuary.

title: Voyeur
description: Legendary journalist Gay Talese unmasks a motel owner who spied on his guests for decades. But his bombshell story soon becomes a scandal of its own.
